replies.body:
Every jungler is good huh.
{{champion:20}} 

I wish, but since Riot gives every jungler utility he will be more useless than they are every time no matter how hard he cj's them. Seriously, too many champs in the jungle just have tons of utility.

I agree with you for the most part but there are a handful of champions who can pretty much only jungle that are performing very poorly. {{champion:77}} {{champion:11}} {{champion:20}} 

Yes they're annoying and a lot of people don't want them buffed, but they are exclusively junglers and they're the only exclusive junglers that are bad junglers at the moment. Nearly every other jungler is either performing well in another role or very close to a 50% winrate and 100% viable in any elo. 

Also, {{champion:266}}  needs to either be retuned as a jungler or buffed if Riot actually expects us to top lane with him.
